<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I participated in numerous forest giants camps in my low 20's, and only saw this thing drop once. When I made 24, I went back to Antonica, made another level, then lost it in Najena. Thoroughly PO'ed, I returned to Warslik Woods with the intention of gaining more levels. <BR>
<BR>
I grouped with an Iksar monk who said he'd killed about a hundred giants and none of them dropped the loop. After our 5th giant death, there was the hoop and i won the roll! Felt kinda bad about it, but greed eventually won out, especially when the monk said it wsa worth about 2K plat.</font></td></tr></table>
